      <description>&lt;p&gt;Have a good end to the year!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;m in Ireland for the holidays making the most of my time off and the awesome hospitality at my girlfriends home.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Next year I am planning to get away at least once for a spot of snowboarding, buy a tv, take first steps into the world of I.T. Architecture, save up loads for a house and possibly brew my own beer.
